extendedInfo.description: You can now BOOK and TRACK your Data Cars minicab on your Android.We cover all South East London including, Lewisham, Abbey Wood, Bermondsey, Bexley, Bexleyheath, Blackheath, Brockley, Bromley, Catford, Charlton, Deptford, Eltham, Greenwich, Lee, Mottingham, New Cross, Peckham, Plumstead, Rotherhithe, Sidcup, Sydenham, Welling & Woolwich.Major destinations are already preset and you can save your favourite addresses.speeding up the process of the booking. Furthermore search for business or residential addresses near to your current location using GPS functionality.Airport bookings and account customers are also catered for:-After booking you will receive a conformation text.
